text: Marshanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Ryazanovsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 83 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Sterlitamak, 4 km from Ryazanovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Marshanovka
